{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idca3dc53d-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598","identifier":"/us/usc/t43/s1511a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1511a"},"text":"§ 1511a.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Cooperation and participation by Secretary of the Army with Federal, State, and local agencies","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of the Army, acting through the Chief of Engineers, is authorized to cooperate and participate with concerned Federal, State, and local agencies in preparing the general plan for the development of the water resources of the western United States authorized by the Colorado River Basin Project Act [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t43/s1501"},"text":"43 U.S.C. 1501","children":[],"tail":" et seq.]."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idca3dc53e-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/611/tII/s203"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–611, title II, § 203","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1970-12-31"},"text":"Dec. 31, 1970","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/84/1828"},"text":"84 Stat. 1828","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idca3dc53f-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idca3dc540-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idca3dc541-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Colorado River Basin Project Act, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/90/537"},"text":"Pub. L. 90–537","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1968-09-30"},"text":"Sept. 30, 1968","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/82/885"},"text":"82 Stat. 885","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to this chapter. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t43/s1501"},"text":"section 1501 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idca3dc542-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was not enacted as part of the Colorado River Basin Project Act which comprises this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
